{"tid":2499950,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「龍門」自選煲仔菜","createTime":"2021-04-22T09:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T09:14:54.000Z","uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83f22368489ab30f5b0b2047a023280ea43eade0","tid":2499950,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPd2FJnk7iiFr81aehH9WJ2uMwCCnPXJeFBxSoDtnQ3sW?filename=6RnTNZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RnTNZW.jpg&h=5e942e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#煲仔菜推介<br />\n<br />\n除咗海鮮受歡迎之外<br />\n煲仔菜其實都好受大家歡迎🤣<br />\n<br />\n當中員工們最鍾意食嘅⋯<br />\n一定係黑椒蜜汁薯仔牛柳煲🤡<br />\n<br />\n事關個汁拎嚟撈飯真係一流<br />\n仲有⋯就係大廚切牛柳嘅時候<br />\n真係名副其實嘅厚切唔留手😰<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議大家嚟到冰室<br />\n一定要嗌呢個餐⋯😎<br />\n<br />\n#豆腐枝竹火腩撈飯食都好LLLLLL<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4f85a8a3d480996faaae6a94c087a337e9615c","tid":2499950,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"唔係執咗咩？<br />\n而家長命過尖沙咀vcd 鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}